D4d7rjDdZKzFBsGNz6F-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SBdD4d7rjDdZKzFBsGNz6F-320-80.jpg\" alt=\"White loft bedroom with white bedding and cushions on it, with a white \u0026#39;COPENHAGEN\u0026#39; print standing on the floor next to the bed\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SBdD4d7rjDdZKzFBsGNz6F-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SBdD4d7rjDdZKzFBsGNz6F-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SBdD4d7rjDdZKzFBsGNz6F-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SBdD4d7rjDdZKzFBsGNz6F-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SBdD4d7rjDdZKzFBsGNz6F-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SBdD4d7rjDdZKzFBsGNz6F-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SBdD4d7rjDdZKzFBsGNz6F-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SBdD4d7rjDdZKzFBsGNz6F-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SBdD4d7rjDdZKzFBsGNz6F.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SBdD4d7rjDdZKzFBsGNz6F.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Future PLC/Anna Stathaki)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eTypically optimising your sleep via sleepmaxxing includes using one of the \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/buying-guide-reviews/best-sleep-gadgets-264989\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/buying-guide-reviews/best-sleep-gadgets-264989\"\u003e\u003cu\u003ebest sleep gadgets\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e like a tracker, introducing black bounds, listening to white noise and more extreme are the ‘sleep girl mocktails’ on social media, which consists of CherryAid and magnesium supplement to help you sleep.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBut some sleep experts are warning that these methods can have an adverse effect on us, and can increase our anxieties towards sleep.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘Trying to follow trends on social media can sometimes cause more harm than good. It\u0026#39;s important to understand that what works for one person may not work for the other. I always advocate to do what works for you and your lifestyle,’ says\u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://malmindergill.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-url=\"https://malmindergill.com/\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-hl-processed=\"none\"\u003e\u003cu\u003e Malminder Gill\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, sleep expert.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-newsletterForm-articleInbodyContent-HS8iwAX96WfpSd3Da2dfuS\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘Following a trend, routine or protocol can put a person into a hypervigilant state, such as obsessing over their sleep, for example. This can actually cause anxiety around sleeping and could end up feeling like a failed attempt.’\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"section-how-to-sleepmaxx-effectively\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHow to sleepmaxx effectively\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eGood sleep hygiene is incredibly important and sleepmaxxing is an effective way to do it - provided you use what works for you. It’s important to note that sleepmaxxing isn’t exactly anything new. It’s a rebrand of recommendations sleep experts have said for yours - with a few social media gimmicks thrown in, too.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D-320-80.jpg\" alt=\"A wall-panelled bedroom with a yellow table lamp on the bedside table next to the bed\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bWXcBTAw9RAZBHnkKUmG9D.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Future PLC/Dominic Blackmore)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eBlack-out blinds are effective at helping you sleep, as well as investing in the \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/buying-guide-reviews/best-mattress-reviews-204596\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/buying-guide-reviews/best-mattress-reviews-204596\"\u003e\u003cu\u003ebest mattress\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e or \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/buying-guide-reviews/best-pillows-282903\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/buying-guide-reviews/best-pillows-282903\"\u003e\u003cu\u003ebest pillow\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e for added comfort and to support the type of sleeper you are.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘A sleep-friendly environment is vital, with research showing that a quieter, darker, cooler room can enhance the quality of our rest. Earplugs, blackout blinds, sleep masks, and appropriate bedding and mattresses are all useful tools that can aid us in this,’ says Joe.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026#39;Sticking to a regular sleep schedule (the time we go to bed and wake up) and reducing screen time before bed are also likely to improve our natural sleep cycle, as our body clock becomes more regular, helping us to release sleep-inducing hormones at the appropriate times.’ \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘Relaxation techniques, such as breathwork, aromatherapy, or calming music, can also help reduce stress and prepare your body for sleep.’\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘Finally, we should all aim to keep our stimulant intake (such as caffeine and alcohol) to moderate or minimal amounts to ensure our nervous system is not overstimulated when we go to bed.’\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv data-id=\"a4b50bde-eb18-40bf-adee-8af59ecf66ee\"\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://target.georiot.com/Proxy.ashx?tsid=107653\u0026amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Famazon.co.uk%2FLumie-Bodyclock-Spark-100-Wake-up%2Fdp%2FB07CN5P1RJ%2Fref%3Dasc_df_B07CN5P1RJ%3Fmcid%3Da3b2ad084dd03aa396cde066bfe0d8f1%26th%3D1%26psc%3D1%26linkCode%3Ddf0%26hvadid%3D697183145910%26hvpos%3D%26hvnetw%3Dg%26hvrand%3D8994065642557285475%26hvpone%3D%26hvptwo%3D%26hvqmt%3D%26hvdev%3Dc%26hvdvcmdl%3D%26hvlocint%3D%26hvlocphy%3